OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for most with rain
OL,6,Fbecoming more widespread through the
OL,7,Fmorning, and some heavier bursts
OL,8,Flikely. A few drier and brighter
OL,9,Fintervals are possible through the
OL,10,Fafternoon, but with further showers,
OL,11,Foccasionally heavy. Breezy, and
OL,12,Ffeeling rather cool.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with showers
OL,15,Fcontinuing through the evening,
OL,16,Fperhaps heavy in the south. Some
OL,17,Fnorthwestern parts perhaps briefly
OL,18,Fdrier before midnight. Winds also
OL,19,Feasing to become light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
